1 Week Ago "As at Sunday, Delta had recorded 1,359 confirmed cases of the pandemic, with 745 of them active, while 31 lives had been lost to the virus. "Ebie thanks Deltans and other Nigerians who prayed for him and had continued to pray for other patients of the virus."